{"word":"ἀνοκωχή","slug":"ἀνοκωχή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n9191\" key=\"a)nokwxh/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνοκωχή</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, redupl. form <sense id=\"n9191.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἀνοχή</ref> </xr> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄκωχα</foreign> <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">pf.</tns> of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔχω</foreign>), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stay, cessation,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κακῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:117\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.117</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. νομῆς</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a stay</tr_> in the spreading of the ulcer, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SD\">SD</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.9</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.8</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n9191.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> esp. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cessation of arms, truce,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δι᾽ ἀνοκωχῆς γίγνεσθαί τινι</foreign> to be at <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">truce</tr_> with one, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:40\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.40</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. ἐστί τινι πρός τιϝα</foreign> one party has <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a truce</tr_> with another, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.32</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n9191.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hindrance,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τριβὴ καὶ ἀ. τῶν Ἐλλήνων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:87\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.87</biblScope></bibl></cit>. (Archaic word used by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> </bibl> acc. to <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Amm.\">Amm.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.3</biblScope></bibl>. Mss. generally have the corrupt form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνακωχή,</foreign> which gave rise to a deriv. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παρὰ τὸ ἄνω τὰς ἀκωκὰς ἔχειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:96:52\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EM\">EM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">96.52</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: but <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> gives the correct form. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0708.tlg001:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ammon.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Diff.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19</biblScope> </bibl> attempts to distinguish the forms.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}